Chic Johnson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chic_Johnson 0 Harold Ogden "Chic" Johnson (March 15, 1891 – February 28, 1962) was the barrel-chested half of the American comedy team of Olsen and Johnson, known for his strangely infectious, high-pitched laugh.
